# Release notes for 1.3.0

[Documentation](https://kubernetes-csi.github.io)

# Changelog since 1.2.0

## Changes by Kind

### Other (Cleanup or Flake)

- Updates Kubernetes dependencies to v1.22.0 ([#165](https://github.com/kubernetes-csi/external-resizer/pull/165), [@chrishenzie](https://github.com/chrishenzie)) [SIG Storage]
- Updates container-storage-interface dependency to v1.5.0 ([#156](https://github.com/kubernetes-csi/external-resizer/pull/156), [@chrishenzie](https://github.com/chrishenzie))

### Feature

- Adds mappings for PV access modes to new CSI access modes: `SINGLE_NODE_SINGLE_WRITER` and `SINGLE_NODE_MULTI_WRITER`. ([#151](https://github.com/kubernetes-csi/external-resizer/pull/151), [@chrishenzie](https://github.com/chrishenzie))
- `leader-election-lease-duration`, `leader-election-renew-deadline` and `leader-election-retry-period` were added to command line arguments to configure leader election options ([#158](https://github.com/kubernetes-csi/external-resizer/pull/158), [@RaunakShah](https://github.com/RaunakShah))

